{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, could you tell Kramer, maybe since we were in the orchestra, maybe he does something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took her back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took her back to-- to the block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she couldn't go outside and stand out in the court to-- to be counted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So then the block leader sent her back to the other camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then again, back-- they brought her back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At the end, she-- OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, my sister, in meantime, she started to feel weak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Her heart was very weak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She-- she stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She ordered-- they ordered that they count her from inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the food was nothing-- so little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because we're all having-- now everybody was having dysentery-- everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If you see the Bergen-Belsen tape-- I have it-- it was a chaos-- skeletons all over the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were all dying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were throwing them on the pits.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They put the prisoners to throwing them in a big pit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the-- those days, what they got is from not eating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't give us-- they didn't have anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They gave us food-- one soup a day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "No-- no-- no-- how do you call-- bread or nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were all getting so thin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of them were having swollen necks-- no swollen legs, and then the neck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If-- if the swelling comes in the neck, it means you're going to die within three days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So every day when we got up, we were looking at our necks to see if it's swollen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No-- we were happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It doesn't matter if we were skeleton, as long as we weren't swollen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- I'm rushing it up, you know, so because of that.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
